title: 216-0732019 Woes
message:
Hi All,

Just wondering if anyone is having much luck with 216-0732019 chips date codes 0937 & 0943 ?

I have also tried 216-0732025 1512 date code. Just cant get a decent chip at the moment. I have 10 here I need to fix asap, with another possible 50 on their way.

Im up shit creek,if there is no decent chips now available. 

I know its not shitty soldering, on my behalf. As I gave a few chips to others, and they have had the same result.

Any alternatives anyone know of?

G

title: 216-0732019 Woes
message: 0937 are fake. The 2015 2025 I used were fine.

title: 216-0732019 Woes
message: Date code 1512 batch code NPW667.00 are the chips I'm using with success.

title: 216-0732019 Woes
message: Thanks duke. I'll hunt these down.

title: 216-0732019 Woes
message: You said you already had 2025 with date code 1512. I'm pretty sure they will be the same chips. Never had any issues with these. 0937 mostly didn't work and the ones that did work came back with video glitches and weirdness.
